reviewText: Wrong movie. I was in the original on IMBd

There is no accusation of murder in this video. This "Other People's Secrets" is an unrated collection of erotic fantasies, with a playful emphasis on B&D in many of the ten stories it tells, ranging from a young innocent trapped with a lesbian dominatrix (much to her eventual delight), to a couple acting out a realistic rape fantasy, to a secretary spanking her boss (after he gets his tie trapped in his desk drawer). It's well-made erotica, and very softcore.
